Developer Terms of Use
des:
Now you can get your daily dose of Stupid News on Alexa! With a simple voice command, hear Rumble in the Morning on FM99 report the weirdest, dumbest, wackiest, and funniest, true news fresh from the front lines of Stupid.
 
The most popular feature on the most popular morning show in Hampton Roads, Stupid News airs every weekday on FM99 WNOR, and now you can hear it on demand with Alexa.
 
So if you missed it the first time, or just want to enjoy it again, just enable the skill and ask Alexa to play Stupid News!
